subproject.description: The project's objective is to demonstrate sustainable approaches for integrating the visually and hearing impaired people into economic and social activities through (i) support the Society of Blind and Deaf in the development of its capacity and services for the disabled; ii) upgrade disabled social and employment-related skills, (iii) integrate disabled into economic activities and (iv) raise public awareness about the potential of disabled to participate productively in the workforce.
donor_long: TURKMEN SOCIETY OF DEAF AND BLIND
subproject.title: Visually and Hearing Impaired
